ype": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/629362711"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI28Dc86yV8OFYEAMaCTEwMjEzNjk1NyCt0KeqBjAAOLsyQAhyCTYyOTM2MjcxMXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1702000294.337758", "card_id": "Q_633714326", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 483}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "江西省民政厅回应「花 10 万买彩票中 2.2 亿」一事，称「正在调查」，该事件或将如何进展？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "「我就是那个快乐 8 大奖得主。」近日，江西一彩民「花 10 万买彩票中 2.2 亿」，引发众多网友关注。12 月 7 日中午，江西省民政厅工作人员告诉现代快报记者，他们已针对此事展开调查工作。 12 月 2 日，江西南昌一彩民在福彩站点，共购买了近 50000 注号码相同的快乐 8 游戏「选七」玩法的彩票。当晚，他所购彩票均中得快乐 8「选七中七」奖项，总奖金达 2 亿多元。据《江西日报》报道，12 月 5 日，中奖彩民来到江西省福彩中心兑奖，并表示：「我就是那个快乐 8 大奖得主」。「花 10 万买彩票中 2.2 亿」引关注，江西省民政厅：正在调查 - 现代快报网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-3eba70a60cb8ec0a9f2507f23fad9223_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "53 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/633714326"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI28Dc86yV8OFYEAMaCTEwMzEwNDAxMCCwmMWrBjAAOJAHQAlyCTYzMzcxNDMyNngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1702000294.338606", "card_id": "Q_531998101", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 650}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么很多人不怕律师函了？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-41f6ad1f5e92068b1c31a5a4982db763_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "52 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/531998101"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I28Dc86yV8OFYEAMaCDgwNTAzNzk3IL6H45MGMAA49A9ACnIJNTMxOTk4MTAxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1702000294.338951", "card_id": "Q_633752669", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 405}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "G7 领导人与泽连斯基发声明，敦促中国施压俄罗斯，要求停止对乌「军事侵略」，对此如何评价？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "（观察者网讯）12 月 6 日，七国集团（G7）领导人和乌克兰总统泽连斯基举行视频会议并发表共同声明。 \t 据香港《南华早报》报道，G7 领导人在声明中敦促中国向俄罗斯施压，以停止对乌克兰的「军事侵略」，美国总统拜登还发布声明感谢 G7 领导人对于乌克兰和以色列的「持久支持」。但在美国国内，国会参议院的共和党人同日否决了一项向乌克兰和以色列提供共计超 1000 亿美元援助的法案。 G7 领导人和泽连斯基举行视频会议，图自白宫推特 G7 发声明敦促中国施压俄罗斯之际，美国国会否决援乌法案"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-778a40ff0e66a05edb9b5eaea8e6fdd2_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "52 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/633752669"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI28Dc86yV8OFYEAMaCTEwMzExMjU1NyDjk8arBjAAOKoFQAtyCTYzMzc1MjY2OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1702000294.339838", "card_id": "Q_633566018", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 200}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "英国塞拉菲尔德核设施被曝出现核泄漏，「官方已掩盖至少三年」，实际情况如何？若属实会带来哪些风险？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "（观察者网讯）日前，英媒炒作中俄相关网络组织「黑进」英国塞拉菲尔德核废料再处理厂，后被英政府澄清。然而，这座「欧洲最危险核设施」面临的真正问题，不在于捕风捉影的「黑客入侵」，而是核泄漏。 \t 12 月 5 日，英国《卫报》援引官方文件披露称，塞拉菲尔德核设施中负责储存有毒放射性废料的储存库 2019 年出现裂缝，已造成「潜在性严重后果」。文件认为，泄漏或持续至 2050 年，若情况继续恶化，可能会污染地下水。有匿名专家透露，有关泄漏的事实和潜在风险已经被官方「牢牢隐藏起来」。 塞拉菲尔德核废料再处理厂，英国政府资料图 \t 塞拉菲尔德核设施位于英格兰西北部、占地 6 平方公里，目前是欧洲规模最大、世界上危险程度最高的核设施之一。冷战期间，塞拉菲尔德原核电厂负责制造生产核武器所需要的钚，也接收意大利、瑞典等其他国家的核废料，当前拥有全球最大的钚藏量。 \t《卫报》报道称，这座拥有数十年历史的欧洲最大核设施出现了一系列安全问题，包括石棉和火灾隐患。但更令人担忧的是，储放有毒放射性废料的储存库外层（由混凝土和沥青组成）出现了裂缝，有毒放射性废料已经泄漏了至少三年之久。 英国塞拉菲尔德核设施被曝出现核泄漏，「官方已掩盖至少三年」"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-222235a3794c6ad39175b53b5c2584e2_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "51 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/633566018"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI28Dc86yV8OFYEAMaCTEwMzA3MTA4NCCuxsCrBjAAOPAEQAxyCTYzMzU2NjAxOHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1702000294.341248", "card_id": "Q_633838811", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 29}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2023 年，能分享下你的职场经历吗?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "毕业后，你的职业发展怎么样，还顺利吗？是从事你就读的专业吗？途中你有过放弃吗？能分享下你的职场经历吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-b5066503bc5137144a93ea77424680f6_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "50 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/633838811"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I28Dc86yV8OFYEAMaCTEwMzEzMTY4OSCb+MerBjAAOB5ADXIJNjMzODM4ODExeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1702000294.341758", "card_id": "Q_633116641", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 74}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为何灭绝师太宁愿摔死，也不愿意让张无忌救她？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-730b8f7f50579be4965d222601031d4f_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "49 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.